
Test "Simple gToken Transfer"
    NewComptroller
    ListedGToken ZRX gZRX initialExchangeRate:1e9
    Prep Geoff Some ZRX gZRX
    Mint Geoff 50e18 gZRX
    -- Just to be sure, check initial balances
    Assert Equal (Erc20 gZRX TokenBalance Geoff) (Exactly 50e9)
    Assert Equal (Erc20 gZRX TokenBalance Torrey) Zero
    -- Just transfer
    Transfer Geoff Torrey 10e9 gZRX
    Assert Equal (Erc20 gZRX TokenBalance Geoff) (Exactly 40e9)
    Assert Equal (Erc20 gZRX TokenBalance Torrey) (Exactly 10e9)

