Test "Simple gToken Transfer Not Allowed by Comptroller"
    NewComptroller
    ListedGToken ZRX gZRX initialExchangeRate:1e0
    Comptroller SetCollateralFactor gZRX 0.1
    EnterMarkets Geoff gZRX
    Prep Geoff Some ZRX gZRX
    Mint Geoff 50e18 gZRX
    -- Just to be sure, check initial balances
    Invariant Remains (Erc20 gZRX TokenBalance Geoff) (Exactly 50e18)
    Invariant Remains (Erc20 gZRX TokenBalance Torrey) Zero
    -- Just transfer
    AllowFailures
    Transfer Geoff Torrey 60e18 gZRX
    Assert Failure COMPTROLLER_REJECTION TRANSFER_COMPTROLLER_REJECTION INSUFFICIENT_LIQUIDITY

Test "Simple gToken Transfer From"
    NewComptroller
    ListedGToken ZRX gZRX initialExchangeRate:1e9
    Prep Geoff Some ZRX gZRX
    Mint Geoff 50e18 gZRX
    -- Just to be sure, check initial balances
    Invariant Remains (Erc20 gZRX TokenBalance Torrey) Zero
    Assert Equal (Erc20 gZRX TokenBalance Geoff) (Exactly 50e9)
    Assert Equal (Erc20 gZRX TokenBalance Coburn) Zero
    -- Add approval
    From Geoff (Erc20 gZRX Approve Torrey 25e9)
    Assert Equal (Erc20 gZRX Allowance Geoff Torrey) (Exactly 25e9)
    -- Perform transfer from
    From Torrey (Erc20 gZRX TransferFrom Geoff Coburn 10e9)
    Assert Equal (Erc20 gZRX TokenBalance Geoff) (Exactly 40e9)
    Assert Equal (Erc20 gZRX TokenBalance Coburn) (Exactly 10e9)
    Assert Equal (Erc20 gZRX Allowance Geoff Torrey) (Exactly 15e9)

